openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: refComponent
  description: refComponent
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.{host}.io/v1
    description: The production API server
    variables:
      host:
        default: openapi
        description: this value is assigned by the service provider
  - url: https://{subdomain}.swagger.io:{port}/{basePath}
    description: The production API server
    variables:
      subdomain:
        default: petstore
        description: this value is assigned by the service provider
      port:
        enum:
          - '8443'
          - '443'
        default: '443'
      basePath:
        default: v2
paths:
  /user:
    post:
      summary: Creates a new user.
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A JSON object containing pet information
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                oneOf:
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Cat'
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Dog'
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Hamster'
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'

components:
  schemas:
    User:
      type: object
      required:
        - userName
      properties:
        userName:
          type: string
        firstName:
          type: string
        lastName:
          type: string
    Pet:
      type: object
      required:
        - userName
      properties:
        userName:
          type: string
        firstName:
          type: string
        lastName:
          type: string
    PetForm:
      type: object
      required:
        - userName
      properties:
        userName:
          type: string
        firstName:
          type: string
        lastName:
          type: string
